{"tid":1632493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論] 小回顧 與 政府決策背後分析 及 運動何去何從","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:40:36.000Z","uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"619c21c635d5f2582790ee4e1aa695e0353ad8ed","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先，老撚老土講句：「各位手足，俾D掌聲自己先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">多謝全球手足；不論前後兩線﹑和勇兩派﹑內外兩域 定係 老中青三代。</span><br />\n無大家既努力﹑犧牲同果敢，場運動就唔會持續到依家﹑世界就唔會關注香港，香港人就未必會覺醒，睇清楚呢個腐敗而醜陋既極權！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>憤怒！</strong></span>絕係係一個令我地撐下去既動力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>犧牲！</strong></span>無數手足以死明志﹑無數手足被捕﹑被毆。我地每一次出黎都係背負住佢地既意志，只許成功！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">信念！</span></strong>我地堅信正義必被申張﹑極權最終定然倒下！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">呢百幾日，香港人不停進化﹑和勇步步升級</span>；我地成功搶佔優勢，愈來愈多中立市民明白示威者既苦心﹑開始轉為支持我地。<br />\n全世界會見到；<br />\nWeConnectED全港各界空前團結﹑大家為公義二字出行；<br />\n最愛返工既港人即使被人阻﹑都會有人出聲支持；<br />\n最守規矩既和理非﹑即使趕住散水搭鐵，都會留錢/買飛；<br />\n示威者點憎政府點憎黑警藍絲黑幫﹑都唔會將怒氣亂咁發洩。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢D所謂既和理非﹑左膠精神，其實正正就係勇武最大既後盾！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但係緊急法推行後﹑大家好似亂左陣腳。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>緊急法前</strong></span>，我地一直慘勝；不停有手足被捕﹑被虐﹑自殺，我地承受住呢一切，大家仍然繼續﹑堅持。因為我地知道：一定要羸！一定要令手足安息！一定要救手足於火海！一定要令壞人受應有既懲罰！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>緊急法後</strong></span>，大家都好憤怒﹑勇武由101後就開始不斷升級升級再升級。的確，所謂既藍絲&quot;好似&quot;怕左。但我地係國際﹑係港內既輿論戰線不斷落敗﹑手足繼續被捕﹑黑警更有理由堂而皇之咁開槍，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>形成N輸局面！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">大家應該係時候停一停，諗一諗初心同目標？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當初勇武為左自衛﹑為左對抗；依家好似更多為左復仇？</strong></span><br />\n的確，仇係要報﹑要十倍百倍奉還！但，沖哂上去打狗，就算打死哂班狗，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>除左快感仲得到乜野？被捕既手足會無罪？受傷既手足會復元？死去既手足會返生？大家要既係五大訴求定純粹真攬炒+N輸？</strong></span><br />\n我地由始至終要既係五大訴求﹑係真普選；定係純粹既癱瘓香港﹑攻擊敵對勢力？就算拆哂全港中資﹑藍絲。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>除左快感仲得到乜野？被捕既手足會無罪？受傷既手足會復原？死去既手足會返生？大家要既係五大訴求定純粹真攬炒+N輸？</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>只有一樣野可以好肯定&ndash;&ndash;被社會離棄﹑中共可以有正當理由出兵﹑國際無辦法出手。</strong></span><br />\n最近呢幾日，大家會好明顯見到連登走向極端，一邊鼓吹極度暴力﹑一邊鼓吹極度左膠；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最終形成分化。</span></strong><br />\n大家好似忘記左當初勇武既共識：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>以武制暴，合法自衛。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">羸左場交﹑輸左個家，值得咩？</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">希望大家嘗試理解一下呢條時間線，然後一齊諗對策！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4zRejz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4zRejz.jpg&h=1f15441b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">政府咁耐以黎，總共出現左一次敷衍﹑兩次軟化，一次加強施壓</span><br />\n唔解釋敷衍果次，我地可以留意到政府兩次軟化主因都係外部；一次係聽證會前夕，希望令美國收聲；一次係竊政70年，希望令局勢降溫。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>而今次施壓呢？其實好明顯，就係希望示威升級﹑令美國同國際</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">收聲</span></strong>！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">點解林鄭多次強調要割暴力席？</span></strong>因為暴力場面去到邊都冇認受性。(亦都係國際撐我地屌黑警既原因)<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>佢明知局勢會更緊張都照做</strong></span>？因為佢(同佢背後既中共)就係想見到有人周圍破壞﹑放火﹑甚至乎打人。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>大家一直以為，咁樣癱瘓交通﹑裝修會令政府驚﹑急﹑錯﹑亂？</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其實呢幾日最開心最安穩就係淋病，因為犬開槍竟然好似講得通喎？市民好似開似出現懷疑﹑搖擺喎？國際輿論開始轉向喎？呢幾日香港市面係混亂，但政府內部實質係羸到開巷。政府目的就係分化﹑孤立﹑擊破，再羸埋國際輿論戰。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n摺被君？其實佢地一早可以出<br />\n裝備精良既犬都足以屠殺市民<br />\n<br />\n佢地唯一懼怕既係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國際有正當理由出手，土共承受唔起經濟嚴重下行時再面對國際制裁</strong></span>﹑呢個亦係點解佢打極貿易戰都輸既原因&ndash;&ndash;佢已經冇本錢。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">所以到呢一刻，佢地想停呢場運動，就要合理化佢地出手既原因；</span>而呢個原因係國際都插唔到手既&ndash;&ndash;例如臨時政府﹑例如大規模破壞﹑傷及平民﹑無底線暴力升級。咁狗/摺被君就有正當理由出手﹑國際亦冇辦法出聲。<br />\n<br />\n暫時我分析到咁多，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府就係希望透過鼓動無底線暴力升級(呢幾日風向)，從而係黃/中立作出分化同拉攏；同時配合Twitter等大量洗版改變國際風向，制造利已輿論。<br />\n亦睇得出政府好急，好想快D係法案前唱衰運動﹑阻止法案通過</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">所以我覺得依家必需要做既係</span>；<span style=\"color: orange;\">重新調整勇武方向，回歸以武制暴；整理多日黎積存既彈藥，大量投入文宣戰；左膠大愛活動亦可考慮</span> (如小組清潔﹑道歉﹑宣傳﹑重建等 ***記得邀請記者朋友見證同時可以保護自己)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">黎緊我地既戰線/大日子好可能係</span>；反蒙面惡法司法覆核﹑香港人權法﹑區議會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地條路仲有好長，急既從來都只係呢個極權政府</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時打到呢度，大家都係手足，大家都真心愛呢個土生土長既香港；<strong>所以我地明知輸﹑都一定要羸！</strong><br />\n希望大家可以回歸理性，從新搵到運動方向<br />\n有錯請指正﹑歡迎理性討論﹑提出意見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBe Humble<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n手足們，我地煲底見，一定。"},{"pid":"2cf226b0cee9e1c080c2a79f1bfef873e7d11e9d","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:14:58.000Z","msg":"兩日冇訓 如果手足覺得岩聽 麻煩幫手推推<br />\n希望聽朝仲會見到呢篇野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bce4b2d1cde2e19cae7807b561c8be33e9c5ec2","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:34:49.000Z","msg":"1，999"},{"pid":"7680d83f33cf006c40f12c8c7e91459d333041c2","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:35:26.000Z","msg":"2，999"},{"pid":"d1ff26dd52a60ad905e0d23dca4b534fdee510a6","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"3，999"},{"pid":"4bc3b0d3e224cfa621b7414da339050db56f4ff9","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:36:25.000Z","msg":"4，999"},{"pid":"c523ef782625ee855111553c0590b06634baa084","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:36:38.000Z","msg":"5，999"},{"pid":"ed04b661d8e0142b862c2711b8036aac5272e261","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:36:49.000Z","msg":"6，999"},{"pid":"13427657164a2924dcd16e28e1e5937df40630c9","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:37:01.000Z","msg":"7，999"},{"pid":"379360cac5756d97e62bfa3c80c1a173b5ebeadc","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:37:11.000Z","msg":"8，999"},{"pid":"35481516d9a7819b175d1d3644f4ac8f18f6b029","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:37:22.000Z","msg":"9，999"},{"pid":"2ac9d25f3ac88f9405f51d28494966393c09c020","tid":1632493,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:37:27.000Z","msg":"可以做形象改善工程<br />\n例如全民捐血、全民義工、全民清潔等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋有大把方法可以取代裝修 唔一定要硬爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnGS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnGS</a>"},{"pid":"3ba4c532565976c85f4347a4d1b9e12904036f8c","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:37:34.000Z","msg":"10，999"},{"pid":"5e0c3469836086c3a5f32c0d04b5b60677d9c2c1","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:38:36.000Z","msg":"11，999"},{"pid":"f49ea65aa3ffabf4fa3fea98112428e90631644c","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:39:28.000Z","msg":"12，999"},{"pid":"39e60f16014f29cec50165aa8a784a03f54cde42","tid":1632493,"uid":245157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:44:36.000Z","msg":"叫「黑警」己無意思，唔好再撚狗硬碰，大家計對的是政權，不是佢守門口隻狗，冇必要辣慶佢咬人，讓牠們留待末日審判"},{"pid":"349acaabbeff908c28d77823e8fc4397aa1b21f6","tid":1632493,"uid":323113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:29:24.000Z","msg":"無錯！政府根本就係想惹到我哋升級再升級<br />\n等我嚟搞到場面好大，又見火燒又見血<br />\n目的有兩個<br />\n1. 想外國人覺得我哋好暴力，<br />\n人權法否決！<br />\n其實佢哋（中共同港共）<br />\n最驚一定係人權法會過<br />\n因為美國過，其他國家都會跟住過<br />\n班官真係驚到pk架<br />\n你要班官成世只可以留係大灣區<br />\n真係比餐餐食屎仲慘<br />\n<br />\n2.政府想11月選舉推遲或取消<br />\n如果能順利選<br />\n大家都知對我哋係最有利<br />\n分分鐘好快就有真普選<br />\n<br />\n所以我真心希望大家冷靜一下<br />\n一切大動作都盡量等人權法過左先<br />\n<br />\n我相信勇和大家係能互相理解的<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港  時事革命」"},{"pid":"2d1ab14dd2da9ef0041d2c5edb43df12afe9be5a","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:37:14.000Z","msg":"1/999"},{"pid":"63db5364ac9baf9a2e670e1d5635f4a6390d227c","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:37:32.000Z","msg":"2/999"},{"pid":"1e6b6c271e9b73217ee0a5b67ca2142eeb57337c","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"3/999"},{"pid":"658229b65b821350df15d693969bb06472158596","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"4/999"},{"pid":"4a9f304c0a5266912871e719377a1e524e460c1d","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:38:12.000Z","msg":"5/999"},{"pid":"585dac98d59a720abdc9e17be3a370001c760d13","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"6/999"},{"pid":"b84650f21b37ad9ce4100d72d1245347433660fe","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"7/999"},{"pid":"45008a66ec753c216bc8f8557fd2ef04059245f2","tid":1632493,"uid":77672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"8/999"}]}